# 🆘 MinePanel GUI Support

If the application does not open or fails to start:

## 1. Check Java
Make sure Java 17+ is installed and available in PATH.

## 2. Check Python
Python 3.10+ is required with Tkinter installed.

## 3. Server not starting
Ensure minecraft-server folder exists and contains a valid server.jar or run.sh configuration.

## 4. GUI not opening
Run the script manually:

Linux:
bash run.sh

Windows:
run.bat (Run as Administrator)

## 5. Logs / errors
Check terminal output or minecraft_panel.log file.
